powertop: PowerTOP (list power consumption of software components)
powertop:
powertop: Intel is proud to announce the PowerTOP tool
powertop: (http://www.linuxpowertop.org), a program that collects the
powertop: various pieces of information from your system and presents an
powertop: overview of how well your laptop is doing in terms of power
powertop: savings. In addition, PowerTOP will provide an indication of
powertop: which tunables and software components are the biggest offenders
powertop: in slurping up your battery time. PowerTOP will update it's
powertop: display frequently so that you can directly see the impact of
powertop: any changes you are making.
